rows.name:
I saw a funny-looking pair get off one
of Acedia's hips.

rows.label: tlk4750016603_msg0002
rows.name:
They sat down here like they were
expecting someone to turn up.
Wonder if they ever did...?

rows.label: tlk4750016603_msg0003
rows.name:
The two of them almost never shut up.
The port's usually so quiet, it was nice
to have some banter for a change.

rows.label: tlk4750016603_msg0004
rows.name:
Hmm? Hold on...it's you! Hahaha!
I had a right laugh at some of your
conversation! Comedy gold!
